  "text": "previously been shown to be associated with CHD, was recently associated with gAgP ( Figure 1 ) [CITATION_1] . The replication analysis in our independent cohort, consisting of 130 gAgP patients and 339 periodontally healthy control subjects without gAgP, strengthened the findings of [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . This result corroborates the idea that the chromosomal locus on 9p21.3 may represent one of the postulated genetic links between CHD and periodontitis. Furthermore, combining the results of Schaefer et al. and our own results in a meta-analysis resulted in an improved statistical power due to the increase in the total number of analyzed individuals.",
